title: Two Whats?! And A Wow! - To the Moon and Back (Encore - 4/15/22)
description:
Why is Mindy gluing her cardboard box together with bubblegum? And what in the world does this have to do with space?! We’ve got questions AND answers for you in this out of this world round of Two Whats?! And A Wow! We’re challenging you to find the fact from the fiction about SPACE! (Originally aired 5/28/21)
